@startuml engine-store
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class VectorStore {
  - _client : PersistentClient
  - _col : Collection
  --
  + __init__(index_path: Path, collection_name: str)
  + add(chunk_id: str, vector: list[float],\n      text: str, metadata: dict) : void
  + delete(chunk_ids: list[str]) : void
  + query(vector: list[float], top_k: int,\n        threshold: float) : list[dict]
  + close() : void
  + __enter__() : VectorStore
  + __exit__(*_) : void
}

note right of VectorStore
  Backend: ChromaDB PersistentClient
  Index space: cosine (HNSW)
  Converts distance → similarity:
    score = 1.0 - dist
  Empty-collection guard in query()
  Context manager for handle cleanup
end note

@enduml
